verbose_text: Our findings suggested that compared with the healthy control group, the expressions of ITGAM, TLR8, IL1beta, MMP9, MPO, FPR2, ELANE, SPI1, and C3AR1 in patients with sepsis were significantly upregulated, which may have an important influence on the pathophysiological mechanism of sepsis.
evidence: expressions of ITGAM, TLR8, IL1beta, MMP9, MPO, FPR2
